data.description: Stunning two-story home in the coveted Sundance at Buckeye, where comfort meets elegance! This home captivates with its desert landscaping, a convenient 2-car garage with additional driveway space, and a front patio to enjoy a morning coffee. The welcoming & bright interior features an open floor plan that seamlessly blends living and dining spaces, ideal for modern lifestyles and entertaining guests. The pristine white kitchen, a true chef's delight, boasts staggered shaker cabinets w/crown moulding, SS appliances, grey-speckled granite countertops, a pantry, and a center island w/a breakfast bar. The versatile main floor hosts a bedroom that can serve as an office or hobby area. Upstairs, the loft offers a flexible space, perfect for a family room or TV lounge. The spacious primary suite has a bathroom w/a dual sinks vanity & a bountiful walk-in closet. With room for a pool, the vast backyard presents a blank canvas to craft your outdoor sanctuary. The extended patio is an ideal backdrop for hosting barbecues or enjoying open-air dining. Excellent location! Short commute to Freedom Elementary, close to restaurants & markets, and easy access to the I-10 Fwy. Don't miss this fantastic value. Act now!
